{
  "texts": [
    "We created a new Amazon Kendra application named \"PUBMED-MM\" to host our RAG chatbot.",
    "The application was configured to use the \"Native Retriever\" as the underlying search engine, which employs sophisticated natural language processing techniques to understand user queries and retrieve the most relevant documents.",
    "We connected the ap-plication to an Amazon S3 data source containing the curated multiple myeloma articles.",
    "To ensure the security and access control of our chatbot, we implemented OAuth 2.0 authentication using Amazon Cognito.",
    "Users are required to sign in using their credentials before accessing the chatbot interface."
  ]
}